Best Foreign Student Award

This award was for graduating with the highest GPA for the graduating class of 2023. it was a recognition of my academic execellence.

Best Computer Science Student Award

This award was in respect to my sterling performance in the field of Computer Science. it was a Departmental award for graduating as the best student from the School of Science and Technology. This award recognizes my competencies in theororical and technical aspects of Computer Science. This award given with a cash prize of 500 Ghana Cedis .

Best Foreign Student Award

Dominion University College has a thriving community of international students. some of the international student came from Nigeria, Togo, Liberia, Ivory Coast, Angola etc. The Best Foreign Student award was in recognition of the academic contributions and diversity foreign students bring to Dominion Univeristy College. This award also reflects my academic performances. In addition to the award, I also won a cash price of 500 Ghana Cedis.

Best Programmer Award

The best Programmer award was awarded by the Students' Representative Council at Exellence Nigth Award and Dinner Night. This award is a recognition of competence in programming skills. Dominion University Students voted for the individual who they believed has shown competency in programming.
